RPM Fusion repository:
sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck https://mirrors.rpmfusion.org/free/el/rpmfusion-free-release-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm https://mirrors.rpmfusion.org/nonfree/el/rpmfusion-nonfree-release-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm

CentOS 8 required additional step:
sudo dnf config-manager --enable crb

AppStream metadata
sudo dnf groupupdate core

Multimedia post-install
sudo dnf groupupdate multimedia --setop="install_weak_deps=False" --exclude=PackageKit-gstreamer-plugin
sudo dnf groupupdate sound-and-video

Tainted repos (odtwarzanie film√≥w z DVD)
sudo dnf install rpmfusion-free-release-tainted
sudo dnf install libdvdcss

Hardware Accelerated Codec with Intel:
sudo dnf install intel-media-driver (from Broadwell)
sudo dnf install libva-intel-driver

Hardware codecs with AMD (mesa):
sudo dnf swap mesa-va-drivers mesa-va-drivers-freeworld
sudo dnf swap mesa-vdpau-drivers mesa-vdpau-drivers-freeworld
i686 for Steam:
sudo dnf swap mesa-va-drivers.i686 mesa-va-drivers-freeworld.i686
sudo dnf swap mesa-vdpau-drivers.i686 mesa-vdpau-drivers-freeworld.i686

Hardware codecs with NVIDIA:
sudo dnf install nvidia-vaapi-driver

Enable Flathub: https://flatpak.org/setup/CentOS/
https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
sudo cp flathub.flatpakrepo /etc/yum.repos.d/

ElRepo Project and EPEL (https://wiki.almalinux.org/repos/Extras.html):
sudo dnf install epel-release
sudo dnf install elrepo-release

NVIDIA Cuda Toolkit: https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-downloads
sudo dnf config-manager --add-repo https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/repos/rhel9/x86_64/cuda-rhel9.repo
sudo dnf clean all
sudo dnf -y module install nvidia-driver:latest-dkms
sudo dnf -y install cuda

Codecs:
sudo dnf install gstreamer1-plugins-* ffmpeg

Thermald:
sudo dnf install thermald
sudo systemctl enable thermald.service
sudo systemctl start thermald.service

Apps:
Google Chrome
Gimp
Audacity
Discord
